metadata.name: sunbathing #01
metadata.description:
It was indeed a very beautiful sunrise: pink, scarlet, and yellow at the same time.  There is not a soul around to such an extent that loneliness becomes absolute and you feel like a part of the world.  You are not and you are everywhere.  Absolute peace, perfect intercourse with yourself.  The point where you're truly happy to be alive.
  It must be that the most beautiful feelings are born at dawn.
